  }, "v7"), mdx("p", null, "Ba-by-l\xF4n nh\u01B0 ch\xE9n v\xE0ng trong tay CH\xDAA, ch\xE9n \u0111\xE3 khi\u1EBFn c\u1EA3 \u0111\u1EA5t say s\u01B0a. C\xE1c d\xE2n t\u1ED9c u\u1ED1ng r\u01B0\u1EE3u c\u1EE7a Ba-by-l\xF4n v\xE0 \u0111i l\u1EA1ng qu\u1EA1ng. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v8"
  }, "v8"), mdx("p", null, "Ba-by-l\xF4n b\u1ECB s\u1EE5p \u0111\u1ED5 v\xE0 b\u1EBB g\xE3y b\u1EA5t th\u1EA7n. H\xE3y k\xEAu kh\xF3c cho n\xF3! H\xE3y l\u1EA5y d\u1EA7u x\u1EE9c ch\u1ED7 \u0111au n\xF3, may ra n\xF3 s\u1EBD \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c l\xE0nh. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v9"
  }, "v9"), mdx("p", null, "C\xE1c d\xE2n ngo\u1EA1i qu\u1ED1c \u1EDF Ba-by-l\xF4n n\xF3i, 'Ch\xFAng t\xF4i t\xECm c\xE1ch ch\u1EEFa tr\u1ECB Ba-by-l\xF4n nh\u01B0ng n\xF3 kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3 l\xE0nh \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c. Cho n\xEAn ch\xFAng t\xF4i \u0111\xE0nh ph\u1EA3i v\u1EC1 x\u1EE9 m\xECnh. S\u1EF1 tr\u1EEBng ph\u1EA1t Ba-by-l\xF4n th\u1EA5u \u0111\u1EBFn tr\u1EDDi; l\xEAn \u0111\u1EBFn t\u1EADn m\xE2y.' "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v10"
  }, "v10"), mdx("p", null, "D\xE2n Giu-\u0111a n\xF3i, 'CH\xDAA ch\u1EE9ng t\u1ECF ch\xFAng ta \u0111\xFAng. H\xE3y \u0111\u1EBFn Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem thu\u1EADt l\u1EA1i \u0111i\u1EC1u CH\xDAA l\xE0 Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF ch\xFAng ta \u0111\xE3 l\xE0m.' "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v11"
  }, "v11"), mdx("p", null, "H\xE3y m\xE0i t\xEAn cho b\xE9n! H\xE3y nh\u1EA5c thu\u1EABn c\u1EE7a ng\u01B0\u01A1i l\xEAn! CH\xDAA \u0111\xE3 gi\u1EE5c gi\xE3 c\xE1c vua c\u1EE7a M\xEA-\u0111i, v\xEC Ng\xE0i mu\u1ED1n ti\xEAu di\u1EC7t Ba-by-l\xF4n. CH\xDAA s\u1EBD tr\u1EEBng ph\u1EA1t ch\xFAng cho x\u1EE9ng v\u1EDBi t\u1ED9i h\u1EE7y ph\xE1 \u0111\u1EC1n th\u1EDD Ng\xE0i. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v12"
  }, "v12"), mdx("p", null, "H\xE3y gi\u01B0\u01A1ng c\u1EDD l\xEAn tr\xEAn c\xE1c v\xE1ch th\xE0nh Ba-by-l\xF4n! H\xE3y mang th\xEAm c\xE1c l\xEDnh g\xE1c. H\xE3y \u0111\u1EB7t l\xEDnh g\xE1c v\xE0o v\u1ECB tr\xED, s\u1EB5n s\xE0ng \u0111\xE1nh \xFAp! CH\xDAA ch\u1EAFc ch\u1EAFn s\u1EBD thi h\xE0nh \u0111i\u1EC1u Ng\xE0i d\u1EF1 \u0111\u1ECBnh v\xE0 \u0111i\u1EC1u Ng\xE0i tuy\xEAn b\u1ED1 s\u1EBD l\xE0m ngh\u1ECBch l\u1EA1i Ba-by-l\xF4n. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v13"
