    "id": "v14"
  }, "v14"), mdx("p", null, "CH\xDAA To\xE0n N\u0103ng \u0111\xE3 nh\xE2n danh m\xECnh m\xE0 th\u1EC1 r\u1EB1ng: 'H\u1EE1i Ba-by-l\xF4n, ta s\u1EBD khi\u1EBFn c\xE1c binh s\u0129 th\xF9 ngh\u1ECBch tr\xE0n ng\u1EADp ng\u01B0\u01A1i, ch\xFAng \u0111\xF4ng nh\u01B0 c\xE0o c\xE0o. Ch\xFAng s\u1EBD \u0111\u1EE9ng tr\xEAn ng\u01B0\u01A1i reo h\xF2 chi\u1EBFn th\u1EAFng.' "), mdx("h6", {
