    "id": "v16"
  }, "v16"), mdx("p", null, "Khi Ng\xE0i g\u1EA7m l\xEAn, c\xE1c ngu\u1ED3n n\u01B0\u1EDBc tr\xEAn tr\u1EDDi vang \u0111\u1ED9ng. Ng\xE0i khi\u1EBFn s\u01B0\u01A1ng m\xF9 b\u1ED1c l\xEAn t\u1EEB c\xE1c g\xF3c \u0111\u1EA5t. Ng\xE0i sai ch\u1EDBp \u0111\u1EBFn v\u1EDBi m\u01B0a v\xE0 mang gi\xF3 ra t\u1EEB c\xE1c kho ch\u1EE9a c\u1EE7a Ng\xE0i. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v17"
  }, "v17"), mdx("p", null, "D\xE2n ch\xFAng k\xE9m hi\u1EC3u bi\u1EBFt v\xE0 ngu d\u1EA1i. C\xE1c th\u1EE3 b\u1EA1c x\u1EA5u h\u1ED5 v\xEC c\xE1c t\u01B0\u1EE3ng ch\u1EA1m m\xECnh, b\u1EDFi ch\xFAng ch\u1EC9 l\xE0 c\xE1c th\u1EA7n gi\u1EA3, kh\xF4ng c\xF3 h\u01A1i th\u1EDF. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v18"
  }, "v18"), mdx("p", null, "Ch\xFAng kh\xF4ng c\xF3 gi\xE1 tr\u1ECB g\xEC; ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ta ch\u1EBF gi\u1EC5u ch\xFAng. Khi \u0111em ra ph\xE2n x\u1EED, ch\xFAng s\u1EBD b\u1ECB ti\xEAu di\u1EC7t. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v19"
  }, "v19"), mdx("p", null, "Nh\u01B0ng Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF, Ng\xE0i l\xE0 gia t\xE0i c\u1EE7a Gia-c\u1ED1p, kh\xF4ng gi\u1ED1ng nh\u01B0 c\xE1c t\u01B0\u1EE3ng ch\u1EA1m. Ng\xE0i l\xE0m n\xEAn m\u1ECDi th\u1EE9, v\xE0 ch\u1ECDn \xCDt-ra-en l\xE0m d\xE2n ri\xEAng cho m\xECnh. Danh Ng\xE0i l\xE0 CH\xDAA To\xE0n N\u0103ng. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v20"
  }, "v20"), mdx("p", null, "C\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i l\xE0 g\u1EADy chi\u1EBFn tranh c\u1EE7a ta, l\xE0 kh\xED gi\u1EDBi \u0111\xE1nh gi\u1EB7c c\u1EE7a ta. Ta d\xF9ng ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\u1EC3 \u0111\u1EADp n\xE1t c\xE1c d\xE2n. Ta d\xF9ng ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\u1EC3 ti\xEAu di\u1EC7t c\xE1c v\u01B0\u01A1ng qu\u1ED1c. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v21"
  }, "v21"), mdx("p", null, "Ta d\xF9ng ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\u1EC3 \u0111\xE8 b\u1EB9p ng\u1EF1a v\xE0 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi c\u1EE1i. Ta d\xF9ng ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\u1EC3 ch\xE0 n\xE1t qu\xE2n xa v\xE0 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111i\u1EC1u khi\u1EC3n. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v22"
  }, "v22"), mdx("p", null, "Ta d\xF9ng ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\u1EC3 ch\xE0 n\xE1t \u0111\xE0n \xF4ng, \u0111\xE0n b\xE0, ng\u01B0\u1EDDi gi\xE0 v\xE0 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi tr\u1EBB. Ta d\xF9ng ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\u1EC3 \u0111\xE8 b\u1EB9p thanh ni\xEAn, thi\u1EBFu n\u1EEF. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v23"
  }, "v23"), mdx("p", null, "Ta d\xF9ng ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\u1EC3 ch\xE0 n\xE1t k\u1EBB ch\u0103n v\xE0 b\u1EA7y chi\xEAn. Ta d\xF9ng ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\u1EC3 ch\xE0 \u0111\u1EA1p n\xF4ng phu v\xE0 tr\xE2u b\xF2. Ta d\xF9ng ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\u1EC3 ch\xE0 \u0111\u1EA1p c\xE1c t\u1ED5ng tr\u1EA5n v\xE0 c\xE1c quan quy\u1EC1n. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v24"
  }, "v24"), mdx("p", null, "Nh\u01B0ng ta s\u1EBD b\xE1o tr\u1EA3 Ba-by-l\xF4n v\xE0 t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 d\xE2n c\u01B0 n\xF3 v\u1EC1 nh\u1EEFng \u0111i\u1EC1u \xE1c ch\xFAng l\xE0m cho Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem tr\u01B0\u1EDBc m\u1EAFt ng\u01B0\u01A1i,\" CH\xDAA ph\xE1n v\u1EADy. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v25"
  }, "v25"), mdx("p", null, "CH\xDAA ph\xE1n, \"H\u1EE1i Ba-by-l\xF4n, ng\u01B0\u01A1i l\xE0 h\xF2n n\xFAi ph\xE1 h\u1EE7y, ta ngh\u1ECBch ng\u01B0\u01A1i. Ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\xE3 ti\xEAu di\u1EC7t c\u1EA3 x\u1EE9. Ta s\u1EBD gi\u01A1 tay ra ngh\u1ECBch ng\u01B0\u01A1i. Ta s\u1EBD x\xF4 ng\u01B0\u01A1i xu\u1ED1ng v\u1EF1c th\u1EB3m, v\xE0 khi\u1EBFn ng\u01B0\u01A1i tr\u1EDF th\xE0nh m\u1ED9t h\xF2n n\xFAi b\u1ECB ch\xE1y \u0111en. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v26"
  }, "v26"), mdx("p", null, "S\u1EBD kh\xF4ng ai t\xECm \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c trong Ba-by-l\xF4n t\u1EA3ng \u0111\xE1 n\xE0o \u0111\u1EE7 l\u1EDBn \u0111\u1EC3 l\xE0m \u0111\xE1 g\xF3c nh\xE0 n\u1EEFa. Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ta s\u1EBD kh\xF4ng c\xF2n l\u1EA5y \u0111\xE1 t\u1EEB Ba-by-l\xF4n \u0111\u1EC3 l\xE0m n\u1EC1n nh\xE0, v\xEC th\xE0nh c\u1EE7a ng\u01B0\u01A1i ch\u1EC9 l\xE0 m\u1ED9t \u0111\u1ED1ng \u0111\u1ED5 n\xE1t \u0111\u1EDDi \u0111\u1EDDi,\" CH\xDAA ph\xE1n v\u1EADy. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v27"
  }, "v27"), mdx("p", null, "\"H\xE3y gi\u01B0\u01A1ng c\u1EDD tr\xEAn x\u1EE9! H\xE3y th\u1ED5i k\xE8n gi\u1EEFa c\xE1c d\xE2n! H\xE3y chu\u1EA9n b\u1ECB c\xE1c d\xE2n \u0111\u1EC3 \u0111\xE1nh Ba-by-l\xF4n. H\xE3y g\u1ECDi c\xE1c n\u01B0\u1EDBc A-ra-r\xE1t, Mi-ni, v\xE0 \xC1ch-k\xEA-n\xE1t \u0111\u1EC3 \u0111\xE1nh n\xF3. H\xE3y ch\u1ECDn m\u1ED9t vi\xEAn t\u01B0 l\u1EC7nh ch\u1EC9 huy \u0111\u1EA1o qu\xE2n \u0111\xE1nh Ba-by-l\xF4n. H\xE3y \u0111\u01B0a ng\u1EF1a ra \u0111\xF4ng v\xF4 s\u1ED1 nh\u01B0 c\xE0o c\xE0o. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v28"
  }, "v28"), mdx("p", null, "H\xE3y chu\u1EA9n b\u1ECB c\xE1c d\xE2n \u0111\xE1nh Ba-by-l\xF4n: c\xE1c vua M\xEA-\u0111i, c\xE1c quan t\u1ED5ng tr\u1EA5n v\xE0 qu\u1EA7n th\u1EA7n ch\xFAng, c\xF9ng m\u1ECDi n\u01B0\u1EDBc m\xE0 ch\xFAng th\u1ED1ng tr\u1ECB. "), mdx("h6", {
