  }, "v29"), mdx("p", null, "\u0110\u1EA5t rung chuy\u1EC3n v\xE0 qu\u1EB1n qu\u1EA1i \u0111au \u0111\u1EDBn, v\xEC CH\xDAA s\u1EBD ra tay l\xE0m \u0111i\u1EC1u Ng\xE0i \u0111\xE3 d\u1EF1 \u0111\u1ECBnh cho Ba-by-l\xF4n. Ng\xE0i s\u1EBD bi\u1EBFn Ba-by-l\xF4n th\xE0nh sa m\u1EA1c hoang vu, kh\xF4ng ai \u1EDF. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v30"
  }, "v30"), mdx("p", null, "C\xE1c chi\u1EBFn s\u0129 Ba-by-l\xF4n \u0111\xE3 ng\u01B0ng \u0111\xE1nh gi\u1EB7c. Ch\xFAng r\xFAt v\xE0o trong c\xE1c th\xE0nh ki\xEAn c\u1ED1. S\u1EE9c m\u1EA1nh ch\xFAng kh\xF4ng c\xF2n, Ch\xFAng ho\u1EA3ng h\u1ED1t nh\u01B0 \u0111\xE0n b\xE0. Nh\xE0 c\u1EEDa Ba-by-l\xF4n \u0111ang b\u1ED1c ch\xE1y. C\xE1c thanh c\xE0i c\u1ED5ng ch\xFAng \u0111\xE3 g\xE3y. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v31"
  }, "v31"), mdx("p", null, "H\u1EBFt s\u1EE9 gi\u1EA3 n\u1EA7y \u0111\u1EBFn s\u1EE9 gi\u1EA3 kh\xE1c; s\u1EE9 gi\u1EA3 n\u1EA7y ti\u1EBFp theo s\u1EE9 gi\u1EA3 kia. Ch\xFAng loan b\xE1o cho vua Ba-by-l\xF4n bi\u1EBFt r\u1EB1ng c\u1EA3 th\xE0nh \u0111\xE3 b\u1ECB chi\u1EBFm. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v32"
  }, "v32"), mdx("p", null, "C\xE1c ch\u1ED7 b\u0103ng qua s\xF4ng \u0111\xE3 b\u1ECB chi\u1EBFm, v\xE0 c\xE1c \u0111\u1EA7m l\u1EA7y \u0111ang b\u1ED1c ch\xE1y. T\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 c\xE1c chi\u1EBFn s\u0129 c\u1EE7a Ba-by-l\xF4n kinh ho\u1EA3ng.\" "), mdx("h6", {
